{
  "stem": "26142.15",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And-- and-- and came back all the way to a city called Miedzyrzec Podlaski.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "That is 50 miles-- 50 miles from Warsaw, between Warsaw and Brest Litovsk.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We stopped there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And also we worked there, loading, unloading, digging, and-- and what not.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] At-- at that place, in Miedzyrzec Podlaski, I found out after the war that this was a-- a 90% Jewish city.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "There were 20,000 people in that city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And there was 18,000 Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It was entirely a Jewish city, with-- with-- with a Jewish police and fire brigades and everything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We didn't know-- we didn't know that when we were there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "In that city, the Germans had a-- a-- they had some booths, steel booths.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And that they would-- they would wash horses in there, would steam them with some kind-- horses that were infected with something.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We also had horses.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And they also had automatic-- those machines that would wash military blankets and whatnot.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And, of course, they were all infected with all kinds of-- of diseases.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And so they-- they used the Jews to do this-- this dirty work for them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Of course, we were dumb.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "At that time, we didn't know that we had to push-- those horses had all kinds of sores on-- on-- on there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And we had to push in these-- in these-- all-- all-- they would lock them up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "All you would-- they would have out is the head and then neck.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And then when washing those-- those blankets and clothing and folding it, and-- and-- and this was full of disease.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I-- I worked there a few days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And one day, I came-- I came from-- from work-- and-- and we stayed in empty houses.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
